<i>And if he can't work...</i>

798
00:49:26.231 --> 00:49:27.265
You got more?

799
00:49:27.365 --> 00:49:28.633
<i>...well. it doesn't last long.</i>

800
00:49:28.766 --> 00:49:30.301
[pounding on door]

801
00:49:30.435 --> 00:49:31.668
[man]
Police!

802
00:49:31.669 --> 00:49:33.471
<i>¡Policía!</i>

803
00:49:33.604 --> 00:49:34.940
Shit.

804
00:49:35.040 --> 00:49:37.909
- ♪ tense music
- [pounding on door]

805
00:49:39.777 --> 00:49:41.479
[snapping fingers]

806
00:49:41.579 --> 00:49:44.349
[man] Open that fucking door.
Chet Davis!

807
00:49:47.618 --> 00:49:48.820
[sighs]

808
00:49:48.920 --> 00:49:50.655
You scared the shit
out of me. brother.

809
00:49:50.755 --> 00:49:53.024
I'm back in the saddle.

810
00:49:54.192 --> 00:49:55.426
Ma'am.

811
00:49:56.461 --> 00:49:58.864
♪ ominous music ♪

812
00:49:58.997 --> 00:50:00.832
- You gonna invite me in?
- Yeah. come in.

813
00:50:02.700 --> 00:50:04.669
Well. this is delightful.

814
00:50:05.503 --> 00:50:07.005
[crickets chirping]

815
00:50:09.540 --> 00:50:11.209
[vehicle approaching]

816
00:50:25.991 --> 00:50:27.425
[engine turns off]

817
00:50:35.433 --> 00:50:36.935
What you up to. honey?

818
00:50:42.007 --> 00:50:43.041
The plan.

819
00:50:43.141 --> 00:50:44.708
Mm.

820
00:50:44.709 --> 00:50:47.879
If we can't afford the life
that we want right now...

821
00:50:48.013 --> 00:50:49.280
Mm-hmm?

822
00:50:51.049 --> 00:50:53.418
...we'll make it work together.

823
00:50:55.786 --> 00:50:57.555
You give me a week.

824
00:50:57.655 --> 00:51:01.259
I'll know everything there is
to know about Beulah Jackson.

825
00:51:02.193 --> 00:51:04.462
Well. let me tell you
about Beulah Jackson.

826
00:51:05.964 --> 00:51:07.765
About three weeks ago.

827
00:51:07.865 --> 00:51:10.435
I found a dead body
on our property.

828
00:51:11.236 --> 00:51:14.105
It floated over
from the 10-Petal.

829
00:51:15.540 --> 00:51:17.075
I took care of it.

830
00:51:18.209 --> 00:51:20.744
But we need
to be careful with this family.

831
00:51:20.745 --> 00:51:23.048
♪ quiet. dramatic music ♪

832
00:51:23.148 --> 00:51:25.016
Why didn't you tell me?

833
00:51:28.519 --> 00:51:30.989
[sighs] Peace. I guess.

834
00:51:33.091 --> 00:51:35.093
Well. peace will have to wait.

835
00:51:37.095 --> 00:51:41.432
♪

